```yaml
---
description: USE WHEN writing or modifying TypeScript code
globs: 
  - "**/*.ts"
  - "**/*.tsx"
alwaysApply: false
---
```

### Agent Requested Domain Rules

```yaml
---
description: USE WHEN writing test files or adding test coverage
globs: 
  - "**/*.test.ts"
  - "**/*.test.tsx"
  - "**/*.spec.ts"
alwaysApply: false
---
```

